room_title: Escape room "Erased" by Ultimate Escape Game in Atlanta
room_address: 3200 Cobb Galleria Parkway, Suite 150 Atlanta, GA 30339
room_description:
In this sequel to the legendary HACKERS room, the location of a sophisticated hackers’ organization has been compromised. They’ve gone into hiding and hired you to “scrub” their facility. Your job is to erase all evidence incriminating your employers.
You have one hour until the feds are beating down the door. Can you erase the hackers’ digital trail in time, or are you the one that will be ERASED?
